data.description: This Perry/medical district stunner has more than one dress to wear to the party! With options to be a spacious single family home or an income producing asset this duplex can easily be converted to a triplex. Home's large parcel has option to be subdivided for additional unit per Spokane building and planning. Fully remodeled main floor showcases a sleek design eye with honey wood laminate flooring, stunning crown moulding accents & pops of modern color. Stainless steel kitchen appliances, large basin sink and hooded gas stove make meal prep a delight! Home is already metered as a duplex with a ground level walk out unit with dedicated access that is framed out for 2 bedrooms. Finishing materials for lower unit convey in sale.
